// and add `sysmlv2 apply-review` — a human-review round-trip where review enters as NEW LINKED
// critique items that attest state + induce computed suspicion (critique_suspect). All at once.
// Total: 8 pts  Ceremony: AUTONOMOUS (D0049); the render+review CHANGE was human-accepted (D0086).
// =====================================================================
package ProjectDeliveryS85 {
    private import EngineElement::*;
    private import EngineWork::*;
